We need to check the rightOperandList also, as it could also contain expressions:
For example:
create table t1 (a1 int, b1 int, c1 int);
create index idx_t1 on t1(a1+1);
create table t2(a2 int, b2 int, c2 int);

splice> explain select a1+1 from t1
> , t2 where a2 in (1, a1+1);
ERROR XJ001: DERBY SQL error: SQLCODE: -1, SQLSTATE: XJ001, SQLERRMC: java.lang.IllegalStateExceptionASSERT FAILED sourceResultSetNumber expected to be >= 0 for null.A1XJ001.U

